<body style="background-color: rgb(39, 37, 37);">
<%- include ('./partials/navbar.ejs') %>
<div class="container">
    <div class="ticker">
        <p>Alert! Brazil's Containment Facility has been Breach, Depolying Group Delta || Warning Sectors 2, 5 & 7 are Under Severe Weather Conditions. Creature's Containment Raised to level 5</p>
    </div>
    <h1 style="color: rgb(77, 77, 235);">
        News
    </h1>
    <div id="carousel" class="carousel slide" data-ride="carousel">
        <ol class="carousel-indicators">
            <li data-target="#carousel" data-slide-to="0" class="active"></li>
            <li data-target="#carousel" data-slide-to="1"></li>
            <li data-target="#carousel" data-slide-to="2"></li>
        </ol>
        <div class="carousel-inner">
            <div class="carousel-item active">
                <img class="d-block w-100" src="/images/cookM.jpeg" alt="First slide">
                    <div class="carousel-caption d-none d-md-block">
                        <h5>Most Wanted</h5>
                        <p>Extremely Dangerous</p>
                        <p>Cookies are at risk!</p>
                    </div>
            </div>
            <div class="carousel-item" style="height: 500px;">
                <img class="d-block w-100" src="/images/mashup.jpeg" alt="Second slide">
                <div class="carousel-caption d-none d-md-block">
                    <h5>Suspiciuos Creatures</h5>
                    <p style="color: red;">Must be 100% Real</p>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="carousel-item">
                <img class="d-block w-100" src="/images/scpClass.webp" alt="Third slide">
                <div class="carousel-caption d-none d-md-block">
                    <h5>SCP Foundation</h5>
                    <p style="color: red;">Classification of Threats</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
        <a class="carousel-control-prev" href="#carousel" role="button" data-slide="prev">
            <span class="carousel-control-prev-icon" aria-hidden="true"></span>
            <span class="sr-only">Previous</span>
        </a>
        <a class="carousel-control-next" href="#carousel" role="button" data-slide="next">
            <span class="carousel-control-next-icon" aria-hidden="true"></span>
            <span class="sr-only">Next</span>
        </a>
    </div>
    <h1 style="color: rgb(77, 77, 235);">
        About
    </h1>
</div>

<div class="container" style="display: flex; margin-top: 20px;">
    <div class="card mb-3" style="max-width: 540px; background-color: antiquewhite;">
        <div class="row g-0">
          <div class="col-md-4">
            <img src="/images/SCP_F.png" class="img-fluid rounded-start" alt="...">
          </div>
          <div class="col-md-8">
            <div class="card-body">
              <h5 class="card-title">Our Mission</h5>
              <p class="card-text">Track and Record every entity unknown to man kind. As well as try to discovery new creatures and make contact with new discoveries. Help humanity with the unknown</p>            
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="card mb-3" style="max-width: 540px; margin-left: 30px; background-color: antiquewhite;">
        <div class="row g-0">
          <div class="col-md-4">
            <img src="/images/gbuster.jpeg" class="img-fluid rounded-start" alt="...">
          </div>
          <div class="col-md-8">
            <div class="card-body">
              <h5 class="card-title">Who are we?</h5>
              <p class="card-text">WE just like to put ourselves in danger, try to save humanity and what not. The scariest part is that we dont make any money from this...</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
</div>    
